txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Dusky wings from the vile crebain found throughout the Lone-lands. The Eglain will honour your efforts should you undertake this task.
'We of the Eglain thank you for this. These creatures appeared before the attacks in our ruins, and we are certain that they are part of the darkness that has swarmed over this land.'
'We have our reasons for our disdain of the crebain. If you are willing to deliver me the wings that you find, it will go far in proving your willingness and your honesty towards the Eglain.'
A task upon the bulletin board requests dusky wings to be brought to Gadaric Munce, a member of the Eglain people located in The Forsaken Inn.
Deliver the dusky wings to Gadaric Munce at The Forsaken Inn
Gadaric Munce of the Eglain posted a desire for dusky wings taken from the crebain that patrol the western Lone-lands. He can be found within The Forsaken Inn.
Wanted: Dusky wings from the vile crebain found throughout the Lone-lands.
